 the same lifecycle event types.\\n     6→\\n     7→## Scope\\n     8→\\n     9→Full feature parity with the Claude Code agent: all lifecycle hooks, HookSupport (auto-install), TranscriptAnalyzer, TranscriptPreparer, TokenCalculator, and SubagentAwareExtractor.\\n    10→\\n    11→## Identity\\n    12→\\n    13→| Field | Value |\\n    14→|-------|-------|\\n    15→| Registry key (`Name()`) | `factoryai-droid` |\\n    16→| Display name (`Type()`) | `Factory AI Droid` |\\n    17→| Description | `Factory AI Droid - agent-native development platform` |\\n    18→| Detection | `.factory/` directory at repo root |\\n    19→| Protected dirs | `[\\\".factory\\\"]` |\\n    20→| Config file | `.factory/settings.json` (project-level) |\\n    21→| Env var (localDev) | `FACTORY_PROJECT_DIR` |\\n    22→\\n    23→## Package Structure\\n    24→\\n    25→```\\n    26→cmd/entire/cli/agent/factoryaidroid/\\n    27→  factoryaidroid.go      # Core Agent implementation + init() registration\\n    28→  lifecycle.go           # ParseHookEvent + compile-time assertions\\n    29→  types.go               # Hook input structs, transcript types, tool constants\\n    30→  hooks.go               # HookSupport + HookHandler implementation\\n    31→  transcript.go          # TranscriptAnalyzer, TokenCalculator, SubagentAwareExtractor\\n    32→  lifecycle_test.go      # Tests for ParseHookEvent (all 9 hook types)\\n    33→  hooks_test.go          # Tests for hook install/uninstall/idempotency\\n    34→  transcript_test.go     # Tests for transcript analysis\\n    35→```\\n    36→\\n    37→## Hook Event Mapping\\n    38→\\n    39→Factory Droid supports 9 hook events. Mapping to normalized lifecycle events:\\n    40→\\n    41→| Factory Droid Hook | Lifecycle Event | Matcher | Notes |\\n    42→|---|---|---|---|\\n    43→| `SessionStart` | `SessionStart` | -- | `source` field: startup/resume/clear/compact |\\n    44→| `UserPromptSubmit` | `TurnStart` | -- | Includes `prompt` field |\\n    45→| `Stop` | `TurnEnd` | -- | Has `stop_hook_active` field |\\n    46→| `SessionEnd` | `SessionEnd` | -- | Includes `reason` field |\\n    47→| `PreToolUse` | `SubagentStart` | `Task` | Sub-droid spawn |\\n    48→| `PostToolUse` | `SubagentEnd` | `Task` | Sub-droid completion |\\n    49→| `SubagentStop` | *(pass-through)* | -- | `nil, nil` return |\\n    50→| `PreCompact` | `Compaction` | -- | Context window compression |\\n    51→| `Notification` | *(pass-through)* | -- | `nil, nil` return |\\n    52→\\n    53→### CLI Subcommands\\n    54→\\n    55→```\\n    56→entire hooks factoryai-droid session-start\\n    57→entire hooks factoryai-droid session-end\\n    58→entire hooks factoryai-droid stop\\n    59→entire hooks factoryai-droid user-prompt-submit\\n    60→entire hooks factoryai-droid pre-tool-use\\n    61→entire hooks factoryai-droid post-tool-use\\n    62→entire hooks factoryai-droid subagent-stop\\n    63→entire hooks factoryai-droid pre-compact\\n    64→entire hooks factoryai-droid notification\\n    65→```\\n    66→\\n    67→## Hook Installation\\n    68→\\n    69→### Installed Hooks (7 total)\\n    70→\\n    71→SessionStart, SessionEnd, Stop, UserPromptSubmit, PreToolUse[Task], PostToolUse[Task], PreCompact. Notification and SubagentStop are not installed (pass-throughs).\\n    72→\\n    73→### Settings File Format\\n    74→\\n    75→```json\\n    76→{\\n    77→  \\\"hooks\\\": {\\n    78→    \\\"SessionStart\\\": [{\\\"matcher\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"hooks\\\": [{\\\"type\\\": \\\"command\\\", \\\"command\\\": \\\"entire hooks factoryai-droid session-start\\\"}]}],\\n    79→    \\\"SessionEnd\\\": [{\\\"matcher\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"hooks\\\": [{\\\"type\\\": \\\"command\\\", \\\"command\\\": \\\"entire hooks factoryai-droid session-end\\\"}]}],\\n    80→    \\\"Stop\\\": [{\\\"matcher\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"hooks\\\": [{\\\"type\\\": \\\"command\\\", \\\"command\\\": \\\"entire hooks factoryai-droid stop\\\"}]}],\\n    81→    \\\"UserPromptSubmit\\\": [{\\\"matcher\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"hooks\\\": [{\\\"type\\\": \\\"command\\\", \\\"command\\\": \\\"entire hooks factoryai-droid user-prompt-submit\\\"}]}],\\n    82→    \\\"PreToolUse\\\": [{\\\"matcher\\\": \\\"Task\\\", \\\"hooks\\\": [{\\\"type\\\": \\\"command\\\", \\\"command\\\": \\\"entire hooks factoryai-droid pre-tool-use\\\"}]}],\\n    83→    \\\"PostToolUse\\\": [{\\\"matcher\\\": \\\"Task\\\", \\\"hooks\\\": [{\\\"type\\\": \\\"command\\\", \\\"command\\\": \\\"entire hooks factoryai-droid post-tool-use\\\"}]}],\\n    84→    \\\"PreCompact\\\": [{\\\"matcher\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"hooks\\\": [{\\\"type\\\": \\\"command\\\", \\\"command\\\": \\\"entire hooks factoryai-droid pre-compact\\\"}]}]\\n    85→  },\\n    86→  \\\"permissions\\\": {\\n    87→    \\\"deny\\\": [\\\"Read(./.entire/metadata/**)\\\"]\\n    88→  }\\n    89→}\\n    90→```\\n    91→\\n    92→### localDev Mode\\n    93→\\n    94→Uses `FACTORY_PROJECT_DIR` env var:\\n    95→```\\n    96→go run ${FACTORY_PROJECT_DIR}/cmd/entire/main.go hooks factoryai-droid stop\\n    97→```\\n    98→\\n    99→## Transcript Analysis\\n   100→\\n   101→Factory Droid uses JSONL format (like Claude Code). Reuses the existing `transcript` package for parsing.\\n   102→\\n   103→**Assumption:** The JSONL schema is compatible with Claude Code's format. If it differs, Factory-specific parsing will be needed.\\n   104→\\n   105→### TranscriptAnalyzer\\n   106→\\n   107→- `GetTranscriptPosition()` -- line count\\n   108→- `ExtractModifiedFilesFromOffset()` -- parse JSONL for file-modification tools\\n   109→- `ExtractPrompts()` -- extract user prompt entries\\n   110→- `ExtractSummary()` -- last assistant text block\\n   111→\\n   112→### TranscriptPreparer\\n   113→\\n   114→- `PrepareTranscript()` -- sentinel-polling for async flush\\n   115→- Sentinel string: `\\\"hooks factoryai-droid stop\\\"`\\n   116→\\n   117→### TokenCalculator\\n   118→\\n   119→- Extract token usage from JSONL entries (if Factory Droid includes usage data)\\n   120→\\n   121→### SubagentAwareExtractor\\n   122→\\n   123→- `ExtractAllModifiedFiles()` -- includes sub-droid transcripts\\n   124→- `CalculateTotalTokenUsage()` -- aggregates across sub-droids\\n   125→\\n   126→## Changes Outside New Package\\n   127→\\n   128→Only one change: blank import in `cmd/entire/cli/commands/` to trigger `init()` registration:\\n   129→\\n   130→```go\\n   131→import _ \\\"github.com/entireio/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/factoryaidroid\\\"\\n   132→```\\n   133→\\n   134→No changes needed to lifecycle dispatcher, hook registry, strategies, setup, or integration tests.\\n   135→\\n   136→## Testing Strategy\\n   137→\\n   138→### lifecycle_test.go\\n   139→\\n   140→- All 9 hook names mapped correctly\\n   141→- Pass-through hooks (SubagentStop, Notification) return `nil, nil`\\n   142→- PreCompact returns Compaction event\\n   143→- Unknown hooks return `nil, nil`\\n   144→- Empty input and malformed JSON return errors\\n   145→\\n   146→### hooks_test.go\\n   147→\\n   148→- Creates `.factory/settings.json` with correct structure\\n   149→- Idempotent installation (second install returns count=0)\\n   150→- Force mode removes existing hooks\\n   151→- Preserves unknown fields in settings file\\n   152→- Uninstall removes only Entire hooks\\n   153→- localDev mode uses `FACTORY_PROJECT_DIR`\\n   154→\\n   155→### transcript_test.go\\n   156→\\n   157→- Extract modified files from JSONL\\n   158→- Extract prompts and summary\\n   159→- Token usage calculation\\n   160→- Chunking and reassembly\\n   161→\\n   162→All tests use `t.Parallel()`.\\n   163→\\n   164→## References\\n   165→\\n   166→- [Factory AI Hooks Reference](https://docs.factory.ai/reference/hooks-reference)\\n   167→- [Factory AI Hooks Guide](https://docs.factory.ai/cli/configuration/hooks-guide)\\n   168→- [Factory AI Settings](https://docs.factory.ai/cli/configuration/settings)\\n   169→- [Factory AI CLI Reference](https://docs.factory.ai/reference/cli-reference)\\n   170→- [droid-sync plugin](https://github.com/yemyat/droid-sync-plugin) (JSONL transcript parsing reference)\\n   171→\"}]},\"uuid\":\"9fe69ad3-8a25-45d6-b89e-f4e0352061a0\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-19T18:17:01.644Z\"},\"normalizedMessages\":[],\"type\":\"agent_progress\",\"prompt\":\"Explore the codebase to understand the Factory AI Droid agent integration. Look at:\\n1. The recent commit `3c37cf55` - what files were changed\\n2. Any files related to \\\"droid\\\" or \\\"factoryai\\\" in the codebase\\n3. The agent integration pattern (how agents like claude-code are registered/used)\\n4. The e2e test setup for agents\\n5. Any configuration or settings related to agents\\n\\nRun `git show --stat 3c37cf55` to see what files changed, then read the key files. Also look at how other agents (like claude-code) are set up for comparison. Report back with a comprehensive summary of what was added/changed for the droid integration.\",\"agentId\":\"ab0e813\"},\"toolUseID\":\"agent_msg_01Kv7rJg5GRUDGLFpoMDgkRR\",\"parentToolUseID\":\"toolu_01C2fRbypBgJmZqTwJc6DPPM\",\"uuid\":\"7f50617a-c9dd-4dec-ac71-b0e18787ca38\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-19T18:17:01.650Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"7f50617a-c9dd-4dec-ac71-b0e18787ca38\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alisha/Projects/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"9a544f58-48c8-4c6e-b193-59716fe328ea\",\"version\":\"2.1.47\",\"gitBranch\":\"alisha/factoryai-agent\",\"slug\":\"harmonic-mixing-ladybug\",\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"message\":{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-19T18:17:04.214Z\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01XkKgdso4TvT4vd1cmAjKTw\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01BTJqojtGPQVf19gqm75ga8\",\"name\":\"Bash\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"find /Users/alisha/Projects/devenv/cli/cmd/entire/cli/e2e_test -type f -name \\\"*.go\\\" | head -10\"},\"caller\":{\"type\":\"direct\"}}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequen