pe:             agentType,\\n   242→\\t\\tTranscriptPath:        transcriptPath,\\n   243→\\t\\tFirstPrompt:           truncatePromptForStorage(userPrompt),\\n   244→\\t}\\n   245→\\n   246→\\tif err := s.saveSessionState(state); err != nil {\\n   247→\\t\\treturn nil, err\\n   248→\\t}\\n   249→\\n   250→\\treturn state, nil\\n   251→}\\n   252→\\n   253→// getShadowBranchNameForCommit returns the shadow branch name for the given base commit and worktree ID.\\n   254→// worktreeID should be empty for the main worktree or the internal git worktree name for linked worktrees.\\n   255→func getShadowBranchNameForCommit(baseCommit, worktreeID string) string {\\n   256→\\treturn checkpoint.ShadowBranchNameForCommit(baseCommit, worktreeID)\\n   257→}\\n   258→\"}]},\"uuid\":\"90c26c30-8546-4e3b-8494-bd50615c6b0d\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-19T20:43:49.981Z\"},\"normalizedMessages\":[],\"type\":\"agent_progress\",\"prompt\":\"Review and simplify the recently modified Factory AI Droid code. The changes span these files:\\n\\n1. `cmd/entire/cli/agent/factoryaidroid/lifecycle.go` - Removed TranscriptPreparer/sentinel code, switched to Droid-specific parser\\n2. `cmd/entire/cli/agent/factoryaidroid/transcript.go` - Added ParseDroidTranscript parser functions, switched internal calls from shared parser\\n3. `cmd/entire/cli/agent/factoryaidroid/transcript_test.go` - Updated test fixtures to Droid JSONL format, added parser tests\\n4. `cmd/entire/cli/lifecycle.go` - Added idempotent session-end handling\\n5. `cmd/entire/cli/strategy/auto_commit.go` - Added Phase initialization\\n6. `cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_session.go` - Added Phase initialization\\n\\nFocus on:\\n- Reducing unnecessary complexity or nesting in the new code\\n- Ensuring consistency with Go idioms and project patterns\\n- Checking for any redundant code or unnecessary abstractions\\n- Verifying the new parser functions are clean and clear\\n- Looking at the ExtractSummary function in lifecycle.go which 